  <title class="- topic/title " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/ai_positron.dita" xtrc="title:1;4:10">Oxygen AI Positron Assistant Add-on</title>
  <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/ai_positron.dita" xtrc="shortdesc:1;5:14">The <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/ai_positron.dita" xtrc="b:1;5:21">Oxygen AI Positron Assistant</b> add-on provides support for helping technical
    documentation writers <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/ai_positron.dita" xtrc="b:2;6:30">generate</b>, <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/ai_positron.dita" xtrc="b:3;6:47">re-write</b> content, <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/ai_positron.dita" xtrc="b:4;6:72">overview</b> and
      <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/ai_positron.dita" xtrc="b:5;7:10">research</b>. It also supports performing AI checks and AI-based modifications on
      <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/ai_positron.dita" xtrc="b:6;8:10">multiple files</b> by integrating AI extensions with XML technologies like
      <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/ai_positron.dita" xtrc="b:7;9:10">Schematron</b> or <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/ai_positron.dita" xtrc="b:8;9:31">XSLT</b>.</shortdesc>
