  <body class="- topic/body " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/ai_positron.dita" xtrc="body:1;23:9">
    <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/ai_positron.dita" xtrc="p:1;24:8">This article is intended to be a general overview of the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/ai_positron.dita" xtrc="b:9;24:68">Oxygen AI Positron Assistant</b>
      add-on installation, licensing, and functionality. </p>
    <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/ai_positron.dita" xtrc="p:2;26:8">We've envisioned this add-on as a way to offer you a personal assistant that contains useful
      actions for checking content (readability, grammar), translating, explaining, and creating
      overviews.</p>
    <object width="560" height="315" data="https://www.youtube.com/embed/-qJZaD_aDMU" outputclass="iframe" class="- topic/object " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/ai_positron.dita" xtrc="object:1;30:77">
